@startuml Activity_Staff_Shifts
title Activity - Staff Shifts

|Staff App|
start
:Open My Shifts;

|StaffOps API|
:Fetch today's/open shifts;
:Return data;

|Staff App|
:Show shift status & actions;

if () then ([Shift change (Start/Stop)])
  if () then ([Not allowed])
    :Show not allowed;
  else ([Allowed])
    |StaffOps API|
    :Apply shift change (start/stop);
    |Staff App|
    :Show success & refresh status;
  endif
else ([Back/Close])
endif

|Staff App|
:Close My Shifts;
stop
@enduml
